Description: Writing documentation is the kryptonite for software engineers. It‚Äôs this thing we have to do after we finish all the interesting work and since we did all the interesting work we know everything about it so why do we need to document it? This idea it‚Äôs definitely exaggerated but I did have a version of these feelings in my first years as a software engineer.
